thread.title_full: Mariners pregame notes and lineups: Two games left in 2015 | The Seattle Times

author: Ryan Divish
title: Mariners pregame notes and lineups: Two games left in 2015
text:
James Paxton said he’ll be ready to pitch when the Arizona Fall League begins. He’s setting up his throwing program for the AFL. Paxton will report to Peoria Oct. 7.
Reliever Tony Zych was also supposed to go to the AFL. But the Mariners may not send him now after throwing so much in his September call-up.
